<title>Practiquemos resolver ecuaciones y representar situaciones con ecuaciones</title>


<!-- ============================================ 
  Objetivos de aprendizaje                        
=================================================  -->

<!-- Frase resumen para estudiante. Originalmente [Student Facing Goals] -->
<introduction component="est-goal"> 
  <p>Resolvamos ecuaciones haciendo lo mismo a cada lado.</p>
</introduction>

<!-- Objetivos para el estudiante. Originalmente [Student-Facing Targets] -->
<objectives component="estudiante">
  <ul>
    <li>[@@@@@@@@]</li>
    <li>I can explain why different equations can describe the same situation.</li>
    <li>I can solve equations that have whole numbers, fractions, and decimals.</li>
  </ul>
</objectives>

<!-- Objetivos que solo ve el profesor. Originalmente [Teacher Facing Goals] -->
<objectives component="profesor">
  <ul>
    <li>[@@@@@@@@@]</li>
    <li>Interpret and coordinate sentences, equations, and diagrams that represent the same addition or multiplication situation.</li>
    <li>Solve equations of the form <m>x + p = q</m> or <m>px = q</m> and explain (in writing) the solution method.</li>
  </ul>
</objectives>


